  "texts": [
    "M B (⟨w 5/3 ⟩, τ) is nonempty if and only if τ = 1.",
    "For both moduli spaces, considering the determinant of the product of the Stokes matrices immediately implies that the condition τ = 1 or τ = 1 is necessary.",
    "It is then possible to check directly that in this case the moduli space is nonempty.",
    "□ Remark 6.4.",
    "Notice that this condition for the moduli spaces to be nonempty is consistent with the sign change of the formal monodromy in the formal Fourier transform."
